    # Make sure the log file is world-readable
    chmod 644 "${LOG_DIR}/access.log"

%labels
    Author DevOps-Apptainer-Setup
    Description Initial state for log-analysis shell task with pytest installed.

%help
    This container supplies the starting environment for the shell task where
    the student must analyse a web-server access log. It contains:
      • /home/user/app/logs/access.log  (populated with sample data)
      • pytest pre-installed for grading purposes.
    The reports directory intentionally does NOT exist yet; students will
    create it during their solution.